Package: longorwide
Type: Package
Title: Data Transformation and Analysis Tools for Wide and Long Formats
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Author", "Name", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for converting between wide and long data formats,
    importing Qualtrics data, reverse scoring items, and conducting common
    statistical analyses including t-tests, ANOVA, and regression. Includes
    a Shiny app for interactive data conversion.
